metadata.description:
Title: "A Night in Yosemite"

Description: This stunning artwork captures the serene beauty of a starry night in Yosemite National Park. Towering trees, rocky mountains, and a calm river provide the perfect backdrop for a sky full of twinkling stars. The use of cool tones and intricate details transport the viewer into the peaceful stillness of the natural world, inviting them to take a moment to appreciate the wonders of our planet.
